{"tid":2296531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"危地馬拉示威者闖國會縱火 不滿削減教育醫療資助","createTime":"2020-11-22T14:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T14:27:33.000Z","uid":82394,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"984cf85c65200c4670fadd1b7a303b4bff84e118","tid":2296531,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:15:56.000Z","msg":"危地馬拉數千名反政府示威者，不滿總統賈馬太及國會削減國內教育及醫療預算，闖入國會大樓並縱火，要求總統賈馬太下台，防暴警察施放催淚彈驅散。<br />\n<br />\n約7,000名示威者先是在國會大樓前聚集示威，不滿國會議員趁颶風不斷及新冠肺肺炎疫情下，暗中通過預算案，無視民意，部分人其後闖入國會大樓，縱火焚燒。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警察向示威者發射催淚彈驅散，消息指有人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n示威者不滿議員向自己批出6.5萬美元（約50.7萬港元）膳食費用，卻削減教育、醫療和照顧新冠肺炎患者及人權機構的資助。副總統卡斯蒂略早前亦曾表明反對預算案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/398c06f76c0e5ceb7a04abcb6c96ca90/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201122/_2020112209291196911.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F398c06f76c0e5ceb7a04abcb6c96ca90%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201122%2F_2020112209291196911.jpg&h=57f14675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/e76a47c5be70c71f6774c087863581b6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20201122/_2020112209291343813.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2Fe76a47c5be70c71f6774c087863581b6%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20201122%2F_2020112209291343813.jpg&h=ab5bb406&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"372c355669f1cfa5d2f3ff07bf242335f11975dd","tid":2296531,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"O多幾個鐘T咪夠錢囉<br />\n係都要出嚟搞亂社會"},{"pid":"92b3e76cc45ea630833fd925534b4fe9b967d578","tid":2296531,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:27:33.000Z","msg":"汁﹕頭條日報"}]}